data.description: *Short Sale - Bank Approved Price* 4 Bedroom 2 Bathroom 2-car Garage Brick Home in highly coveted private Northeast Tallahassee Location! Price reflects Home could use some Updates. Interior boasts a 4/2, 1800sf, sizeable Living Area overlooking a Private Backyard, separate Dining Area, large Indoor Pantry/Laundry Room, large Kitchen, with Breakfast Nook/Home Office Area and Window Shutters. Outside Offers: Quiet No-Thru Private Street, huge Fenced Backyard, 20' x 12' Covered Brick Patio, Shed, Irrigation system, with Mature Landscaping.
